<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Gerando PDF – TalentX</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: #0f172a; /* fundo escuro */
      color: #f1f5f9;       /* texto claro */
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1, h5 {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .progress {
      height: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .instagram-box {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #22d3ee;
      border: none;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #06b6d4;
    }

    iframe {
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 2px solid #334155;
    }

    /* Efeito pulsante */
    .pulsing {
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.85; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>⏳ Estamos finalizando seu currículo!</h1>
  <p>Aguarde alguns segundos. Seu PDF está sendo preparado.</p>

  <div class="progress w-75 mx-auto">
    <div id="progressBar" class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-info"
         role="progressbar" style="width: 0%">0%</div>
  </div>

  <div class="instagram-box">
    <h5>Acompanhe mais oportunidades e dicas no nosso Instagram!</h5>
    <p>Siga e tenha acesso a vagas quentinhas!</p>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/talentx.curriculo" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary pulsing">
      Seguir @talentx.curiculo no Instagram
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4">
    <p><strong>Veja uma das nossas dicas mais recentes:</strong></p>
    <iframe
      src="https://www.instagram.com/p/DJxtLkXslcO/embed"
      width="320"
      height="400"
      frameborder="0"
      scrolling="no"
      allowtransparency="true">
    </iframe>
  </div>

  <script>
    let progress = 0;
    const bar = document.getElementById('progressBar');
    const interval = setInterval(() => {
      progress += 2;
      bar.style.width = `${progress}%`;
      bar.textContent = `${progress}%`;

      if (progress >= 100) {
        clearInterval(interval);
        window.location.href = "/download-pdf";
      }
    }, 100);
  </script>

</body>
</html>
